## Summary
This documentation details the server-side Google Tag Manager (GTM) template for Amplitude Analytics, which uses the HTTP V2 API for data collection. It covers container setup, template configuration, event mapping, user property tracking, and explains how to properly configure API keys, event properties, user properties, and triggers for sending data to Amplitude.

